<chapter id="chapter.regexp">
  <title>Expressiones regular<indexterm class="singular">
      <primary>Expressiones regular</primary> <seealso>Segmentation</seealso> <seealso>Cerca</seealso>
    </indexterm></title>

  <para>Le expressiones regular (o in breve regex) usate in le regulas de recercas e de segmentation, es illos supportate per Java. Si tu deberea necessitar information plus specific, consulta le <ulink url="http://download.oracle.com/javase/1.6.0/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html">documentation Regex Java</ulink>. Vide referentias additional e exemplos successivemente.</para>

  <note>
    <para>Iste capitulo es designate pro usatores experte, que debe definir lor proprie variantes de regulas de segmentation o imaginar elementos clave de recerca plus complexe e potente.</para>
  </note>

